    4 Bed

    Big Moon Cottage is a detached house on a .9 acre site in West Cork on The Wild Atlantic Way. The house is 20-30 mins walk to beach (see local beach Sandycove in attached photo) and 9 minutes drive to the market town of Skibbereen. This is a tastefully restored and extended traditional cottage, packed with character and original features, a much-loved home. \r\n\r\nThere is HIGH SPEEED BROADBAND at the house and business high speed packages are available from our area provider, Rapid Broadband.\r\n\r\nFrom all South-facing front windows in the house there is a wonderful panoramic countryside vista (see photos) with a tiny sea view on a clear day! This is a home of tranquility with the 'buzz' of the market town of Skibbereen so close by.\r\n\r\nThis area is magical countryside for those seeking a beautiful location close to the coast.\r\n\r\nThe property is 1,500 sq ft (139.35 Mt sq) on a site of .9 acre. \r\n\r\nHighlights of Property: \r\n\r\nNews\r\nNew condenser boiler installed January 2021 and new immersion water heater installed 2020, see photos. Lighting has been given particular attention. \r\n- Good-sized utility room, tiled floor with fitted solid pine white painted 'cottage style' cabinets, sink and new washing machine and space for dryer, easily converted to a second kitchen (double aspect). Large pine shelf on one wall. \r\n- Good sized shed with window and shelves. \r\n- Attractive mature garden which is fairly low maintenance\r\n- Phone points in sitting room, snug (2 phone points, one for phone and one for Sky tv), kitchen and master bedroom. \r\n- Good supply of electrical sockets for lamps, music systems, etc. throughout house. \r\n- Pine tongue & groove ceilings in kitchen, sun room and 4th bedroom, painted white. White painted original tongue and groove ceiling in bedroom 3 which also has very attractive cottage style built in units along entire length of one wall. \r\n- Built-in wardrobes in 3 bedrooms. \r\n- 2 en-suite bathrooms with electric showers. Main bathroom downstairs has a shower (with excellent pressure) over a good size enamel bath which is in very good condition. There is also a large wash-hand basin with a big built in mirror behind it with light over mirror.
